  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Ventral hernias, primary and recurrent, are major surgical challenge. We aim to investigate
      efficacy of modified technique of ventral hernias repair: an &quot;open intraperitoneal mesh&quot;
      technique.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
